-- Ashok Leyland Rated `Buy' in New Coverage at Goldman on Capacity, Demand
-- Shiyin Chen
-- 2010-07-12T00:29:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/ashok-leyland-rated-buy-in-new-coverage-at-goldman-on-capacity-demand.html

          
          
             Ashok Leyland Ltd. was rated “buy”
in new coverage by Goldman Sachs Group Inc. analyst Sandeep
Pandya, who said increasing capacity and demand will drive
volume growth and returns.  
 The analyst has a share-price estimate of 82 rupees.  
